CMakeLists.txt

main.cpp contents:
```
#include "project-sim/project-sim.hpp"

int main() {
    std::cout << "Hello world from main.exe" << std::endl;

    // Defined in project-sim.hpp/cpp. 
    // std::cout << "Hello world from Project-Sim" << std::endl;
    printSim();
}
```

Building:
```
cmake -P devops/project.cmake debug
```

Executing:
```
./builds/project/Debug/project-exe
```

Execution Output:
```
Hello world from main.exe
Hello world from Project-sim
```

